	 • Live refresh badge on player buttons (plant count)
	 • Stat bar: shows total plants + mutation count in current view
	 • Keyboard shortcut: R to reopen GUI
	 • Mobile-friendly reopen button
	 • Cleaner layout, no magic numbers scattered everywhere
--]]

